<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><entry xmlns:functx="http://www.functx.com" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_fædæg" xml:lang="os-x-iron"><form type="lemma"><orth>fædæg</orth></form><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>сосок</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>nipple</q></cit></sense><cit type="exampleGroup"><cit type="example"><quote>xæram myn wæd dæ fædæg</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>да будет мне не впрок (молоко) твоего сосца</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>let the milk of your nipple be not for my good</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Сека"/><biblScope>25</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><cit type="exampleGroup"><cit type="example"><quote>xæram myn wæd dæ fædæg</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>да будет мне не впрок (молоко) твоего сосца</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>let the milk of your nipple be not for my good</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Сека"/><biblScope>25</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно, восходит к <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>*pātaka-</w></mentioned> от корня <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>рā-</w><gloss><q>пить</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/><gloss><q>сосать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">в каузативе</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">causative</note><gloss><q>поить</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/><gloss><q>кормить</q></gloss></mentioned>,  (стало быть, образование такое же, как в русском %iсосок%i от %iсосать%i). Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/><w>pātā-</w><gloss><q>выпитое</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="kho"><w/><gloss><q>питье</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/><w>рā-</w><gloss><q>пить</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/><gloss><q>сосать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/><gloss><q>поить</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>pātra-, pātraka</w><gloss><q>сосуд</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/><w>pōtus</w><gloss><q>питье</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="la"><w>pōto, pōtāre</w><gloss><q>пить</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/><w>πότσς</w><gloss><q>питье</q></gloss></mentioned>. Этот же корень, вероятно, в <ref type="xr" target="#entry_fæzdon"/> ‘вымя’ (из %i*pāt-dān%i). Ср. также <ref type="xr" target="#entry_syvædæg"/> (из %isy-fædæg%i) ‘роговая соска’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_mængvædæg"/> (← %imæng-fædæg%i) ‘курок’ („ложный сосок“).</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It probably traces back to <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>*pātaka-</w></mentioned> from the root <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>рā-</w><gloss><q>пить</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/><gloss><q>suck</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">в каузативе</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">causative</note><gloss><q>give to drink</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w/><gloss><q>feed</q></gloss></mentioned>,  (thus, the derivation pattern is the same as in Russian %iсосок%i ‘nipple’ from %iсосать%i ‘suck’). Cf. <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/><w>pātā-</w><gloss><q>drunk liquid</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="kho"><w/><gloss><q>drinking</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/><w>рā-</w><gloss><q>drink</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/><gloss><q>suck</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/><gloss><q>give to drink</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>pātra-, pātraka</w><gloss><q>vessel</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/><w>pōtus</w><gloss><q>drinking</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="la"><w>pōto, pōtāre</w><gloss><q>drink</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/><w>πότσς</w><gloss><q>drinking</q></gloss></mentioned>. The same root is probably in <ref type="xr" target="#entry_fæzdon"/> ‘udder’ (from %i*pāt-dān%i). Cf. also <ref type="xr" target="#entry_syvædæg"/> (from %isy-fædæg%i) ‘pacifier made out of a horn’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_mængvædæg"/> (← %imæng-fædæg%i) ‘cocking piece’ (literally ‘false nipple’).</etym></entry>